Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{is a world we cyborgs created.}là do các Cyborg tạo ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Gadoll are produced here}Gadoll được sản xuất ở đây
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{and programmed to attack Deca-dence.}và lên chương trình tấn công Deca-Dence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{To us, the fight with the Gadoll}Với bọn chú, chiến đấu với Gadoll,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{is nothing but a game to--}không khác gì ngoài việc chơi game--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Natsume!}Này Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Natsume! Come on. Wake up!}Natsume! Tỉnh lại đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{What happened?!}Chuyện gì đã xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't know!}Chẳng biết luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Whatever it was, it's bad!}Nguy quá! Nguy quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is bad!}Tệ rồi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do we do?}Chúng ta lam gì giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is a huge emergency!}Tình hình cực kì nguy cấp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! Why the hell is the GGS active?}Chết iệt! Tại sao GGS lại khởi động?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{A-A-At this rate, we'll lose\Nevery Gadoll in Deca-dence!}C-C-Cứ thế này chúng ta sẽ \Nmất toàn bộ Gadoll ở Dece-Dence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do we do? What do we do? What do we--}Làm sao đây? Làm sao đây? Làm sao--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can it! I've told you not to lose your cool!}Im đi! Đừng mất bình tĩnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do we do?}Chúng ta làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{No way...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even the Gadoll factory?!}Ngay cả nhà máy Gadoll?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do we do?!}Chúng ta phải làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shit!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Those damn bugs!}Lũ lỗi chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's the holdup?}Vẫn chưa nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Data transfer completed!}Dữ liệu đã chuyển xong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{Good. Let's log out.}Tốt. Đăng xuất thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{What about him?}Còn nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Leave him. He's dying.}Kệ đi. Nó sắp chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{That hurt, you piece of shit!}Đau đấy con khốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's go.}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{That left damned marks.}Dám cắn cả mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{The hell was that?}Thứ chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{They're disintegrating?}Nó đang tan biến?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{What did this?}Rốt cuộc là chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Natsume, you did it, didn't you?}Natsume, em đã làm được rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{They're dying off on their own!}Tự nhiên chúng lăn ra chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's gotta be a bug.}Lỗi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come on! For real, what's the deal?}Này này, chuyện gì đang xảy ra thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's completely bugged!}Chắc chắn là lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Service Disruption Announcement"\N"(Error Code 0440)"}Lỗi 0440
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Service Disruption Announcement"\N"(Error Code 0440)"\NDue to error code 0440,\Nservice will be temporarily halted.}Do mã lỗi 0440 nên trò chơi sẽ tạm ngừng hoạt động.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Service Disruption Announcement"\N"(Error Code 0440)"\NDue to error code 0440,\Nservice will be temporarily halted.}Do mã lỗi 0440 nên trò chơi sẽ tạm ngừng hoạt động.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please wait until it is restored.}Hãy chờ đến khi khôi phục.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh come on. That's no fun.}Thiệt tình, chán chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well this sucks.}Nhảm thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Commander, what should we do?}Chỉ huy, chúng ta phải làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Should we go on standby for now?}Chuyển sang chế độ chờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Who knows. Ask the system.}Ai biết. Đi mà hỏi hệ thống.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{what do you plan to do?}cậu định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{No... No!}Không... không!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your wounds...}Vết thương của chú...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{So it wasn't a dream.}Quả nhiên không phải là mơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{We don't dream... unlike you humans.}Bọn chú không mơ... như nhân loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{We have to tell the others ASAP.}Cháu phải nói cho mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can't.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{The truth of the world\Nis off limits to you humans.}Sự thật về thế giới này là quá sức với nhân loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Humans who learn the truth...\NThe world does not permit such bugs.}Nếu con người biết sự thật...\N Thế giới phải sạch bóng lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Ý chú là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're the only exception.}Cháu là ngoại lệ duy nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{B-But--}N-Nhưng--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Do you think I'm lying?}Cháu nghĩ chú đang nói dối à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngay cả cha cháu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What is this?!}Đ-Đây là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Muro, it's exactly as you said.}Muro, y như cậu nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. There's something strange about our world.}Phải, có gì đó kì lạ ở thế giới chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Some hidden secret...}Một bí mật ẩn giấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Stay strong!}Bình tĩnh nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're going back home, okay?}Con sẽ quay lại Deca-Dence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Natsume, Daddy's gonna be back soon, okay?}Natsume, ba sẽ quay về sớm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait for me.}Chờ ba nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{He got too close to the truth.}Cậu ta đã tiến gần đến sự thật của thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{So he was deemed a bug and killed.}Thế nên bị xác định là lỗi và xóa bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{So then,}Vậy chú,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{you knew, didn't you, Boss?}biết mọi chuyện nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{About the Gadoll,}Về Gadoll,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{about the world...}về thế giới...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{...about my father.}...về ba cháu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{That means you've been\Ndeceiving me the whole time.}Chú đã luôn giấu cháu suốt thời gian qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{I--}Chú--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{What I wanted wasn't to change the world.}Những gì cháu muốn không phải là thay đổi thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{What I wanted was to have confidence.}Mà chỉ là muốn tự tin hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{I thought, if I worked hard to\Nget stronger, I might change.}Cháu nghĩ rằng nếu tiếp tục\N chăm chỉ thì có thể sẽ thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now I feel stupid.}Giờ cháu cảm thấy thật ngu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{If this is the truth,\NI would've rather stayed ignorant.}Nếu đây là sự thật, cháu thà cứ mãi u mê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nothing needed to change.}Không cần phải thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{I never should've}Cháu không nên
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{trusted you.}tin chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Boss, don't worry about Pipe.\NI promise I'll take great care of him!\NSo l̶e̶t̶ ̶m̶e̶ ̶k̶n̶o̶w̶ ̶a̶s̶ ̶s̶o̶o̶n̶ ̶a̶s̶\Ny̶o̶u̶ ̶g̶e̶t̶ ̶b̶a̶c̶k̶!̶ Natsume"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"I promise I'll take great care of him!\NSo l̶e̶t̶ ̶m̶e̶ ̶k̶n̶o̶w̶ ̶a̶s̶ ̶s̶o̶o̶n̶ ̶a̶s̶\Ny̶o̶u̶ ̶g̶e̶t̶ ̶b̶a̶c̶k̶!̶ Natsume"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"To Boss"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Cheers!}Cạn ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Drink up!}Uống đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's get drunk today!}Không say không về!
