Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{We can go where we want and do what we want!}Thích đi đâu thì đi, ở đâu thì ở.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{We're free!}Chúng ta tự do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tự do và hòa bình!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{All right, another round!}Uống nữa nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing over here?}Em làm gì ngoài này?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad you're okay. Welcome back.}May mà em trở về an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come on! Let's go!}Nào! Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{What am I doing?}Mình làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{What was all my effort even for?}Tất cả nỗ lực của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Jill"}Jill
