Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Registered Bug Gear" "Bug Record"\N"Jill"\NRegardless, we've been fully designated as bugs.}{"Registered Bug Gear" "Bug Record"\N"Kaburagi"\NRegardless, we've been fully designated as bugs.}Cơ mà chúng ta được xem hoàn toàn là lỗi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Registered Bug Gear" "Bug Record"\N"Donatello"\NRegardless, we've been fully designated as bugs.}{"Registered Bug Gear" "Bug Record"\N"Kaburagi"\NRegardless, we've been fully designated as bugs.}Cơ mà chúng ta được xem hoàn toàn là lỗi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Registered Bug Tanker" "Bug Record"\N"Natsume"\NRegardless, we've been fully designated as bugs.}{"Registered Bug Gear" "Bug Record"\N"Kaburagi"\NRegardless, we've been fully designated as bugs.}Cơ mà chúng ta được xem hoàn toàn là lỗi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have to log in! Please, Jill!}Tôi phải đăng nhập ngay! Jill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{What? We can't do it here.}Hả? Ở đây sao đăng nhập được?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{We have to reach the hideout.}Phải đến nơi trú ẩn tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't drink any more!}Hết uống nổi rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not done yet.}Vẫn chưa đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is the best!}Tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's this?}Cái gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Kaburagi"}Kaburagi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Boss!}Ông chủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{"I am deeply sorry I couldn't\Nbe honest with you all this time."}"Chú rất xin lỗi vì không thể nói cháu nghe sự thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{At the same time, I regret\Nhurting you by telling you the truth.}Và cũng hối hận vì đã nói cháu nghe sự thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{I lived my life deceiving you humans.}Chú đã sống cả cuộc đời để lừa dối nhân loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{That was part of the rules of the world.}Đó là một phần quy luật của thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{I just turned a blind eye to the fact that\Nupholding the rules brought suffering to others.}Chú đã nhắm mắt làm ngơ khi \Nnhững luật lệ đó khiến người khác đau khổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was normal.}Đó là điều hiển nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{When I first met you,}Lần đầu gặp cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{I had no attachment to life.}Chú chẳng quan tâm đến việc sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{I had no attachment to life.}Chú chẳng quan tâm đến việc sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Please Refill Oxyone"\N"Time until scrapping: 175 years"\NI intended to die.}Chú đã định chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe I was trying to find some\Nsmall peace by abandoning life.}Có lẽ chú muốn tìm một nơi bình yên\N bằng việc thoát khỏi sự sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe I was trying to find some\Nsmall peace by abandoning life.}Có lẽ chú muốn tìm một nơi bình yên\N bằng việc thoát khỏi sự sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{But, after seeing the way you\Nlived your life, I was captivated by it.}Nhưng sau khi thấy cách cháu sống, \Nchú đã được tiếp thêm động lực.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{I decided to try pushing myself to my limits.}Chú quyết định đẩy bản thân đến giới hạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've decided to work to\Ndestroy the rules of this world.}Và sẽ tiếp tục phá hủy luật lệ của thế giới này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{I believe that's at least\Nwhat I can do to atone.}Chú tin rằng đó là việc mình có thể làm để chuộc lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want you to live your life as you see fit.}Chú muốn cháu sống theo cách bản thân muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{"You'll be all right.\NKaburagi"}Cháu sẽ ổn thôi."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{"You'll be all right.\NKaburagi"}Cháu sẽ ổn thôi."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{"You'll be all right.\NKaburagi"}Cháu sẽ ổn thôi."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{What the hell?!}Cái quái gì thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Old Deca-dence parts, huh?}Dece-Dence cũ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{--This is nice.\N--Isn't this awesome?}Nơi này tuyệt ghê!\N Tuyệt thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{We'll definitely be safe here.}Chúng ta sẽ an toàn ở đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{What're you two doing?}Hai người làm trò gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{There ain't even any Gadoll. Why log in?}Có Gadoll đâu mà đăng nhập?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Jill, can't you go faster?!}Jill, vẫn chưa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is the problem with you guys.}Thiệt tình, phải từ từ chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please be safe!}Hãy an toàn nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Boss! You're here, aren't you?}Ông chủ! Chú có ở đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Boss, I'm coming in!}Cháu vào nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ow.}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Boss! A-A-Are you okay?}C-Chú ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Boss, I read your letter.}Cháu đã đọc bức thư.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{What was that about?}Vậy là sao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{I got what you wanted to tell me, but...}Cháu biết những gì chú muốn nói nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you planning to leave again?}Chú lại định đi xa nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm about to--}Chú đang định--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{How can you be so selfish?!}Sao chú có thể ích kỷ như vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{You just write what you want to say and run?!}Viết thư trăn trối xong bỏ chạy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{And where do you get off with,\N"You'll be all right"?!}Rồi cái gì mà "Cháu sẽ ổn thôi" nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not right at all!}Cháu không ổn chút nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{I won't be all right...}Cháu không ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Chú xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was a shock, that I had been\Ndeceived for so long.}Nó thật là sốc. Cháu đã bị lừa dối quá lâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{But the time I spent with you,}Nhưng khoảng thời gian bên chú...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{the fights we fought,}những trận chiến chúng ta cùng nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{the things we did weren't lies.}những điều đó không phải dối trá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{I decide for myself, right?}Chú sẽ tự quyết định nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{And so}Thế nên cháu sẽ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I choose to trust you, the person I know.}chọn tin vào chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Boss, if you're gonna fight these "rules,"}Ông chủ, nếu chú đang chiến đấu chống lại cái "luật lệ" đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{you'll have my help.}cháu sẽ giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's--}Hãy cùng--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{B-Boss!}C-Chú!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{So you came here, just as I predicted.}Quả nhiên ngươi đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You }{\i0}{won't escape either.}Giờ thì cả ngươi cũng đừng hòng thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{The world must be rid of bugs.}Thế giới phải sạch bóng lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Jill, can't you do something?}Jill, có làm được gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, I can't.}Không được rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's impossible to log in to your avatar.}Không thể đăng nhập vào tài khoản của anh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have to help or she'll...}Tôi phải cứu con bé...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{What was that noise?}Âm thanh gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, look...}Nhìn kìa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{What }{\i1}{is }{\i0}{that?}Thứ gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{How?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{So it's }{\i1}{not }{\i0}{over.}Vẫn chưa kết thúc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{They sure don't disappoint!}Đừng làm ta thất vọng đấy!
